Accounts Assistant (4 months contract)
Location:  Singapore
Salary:  CompetitiveThe CompanyOur client is a MNC which has presence in Europe, America and Asia. They provide analysis and advice on assets, companies as well as markets. Looking to expand APAC operations, our client is actively sourcing for outstanding professionals to join their team. The RoleFor this role, you will be handling both AP and AR functions. You are expected to process claims, invoices and other payments and also ensure that AR receipts are properly recorded. You should also support the Finance Manager in month end closing. Your ProfileYou should have at least a Diploma or equivalent, with minimum 3 years of experience working in the accounting field, preferably from MNC background. You should have good communications skills and are able to work independently. Immediate availability preferred.Apply TodayPlease send your resume, in WORD format and quote reference number Ref No ET11796, by clicking the apply button. Please note that only short-listed candidates will be contacted.
